# Make some folders in which to store our Vagrant VMs.
mkdir centos-7 ubuntu-xenial64
# Create the centos-7/Vagrantfile file.
vagrant init -m --output centos-7/Vagrantfile centos/7
# Create the ubuntu-xenial64/Vagrantfile file.
vagrant init -m --output ubuntu-xenial64/Vagrantfile ubuntu/xenial64
